    "4011310": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Idyia",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey Idyia, you got an update for us? We've all caught up with each other."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Very well. Then please allow me, Idyia, your Mascot, to explain exactly what's happened here..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(She's pretty happy with this Mascot role, huh...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Basically, this entire domain is powered by a device called the Central Hub, which you all saw earlier."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "But following a major incident, several key components from the Central Hub came loose and went flying."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "...Four components, I believe, which has caused the Central Hub to stop turning."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Ohhh, so that thing's supposed to spin?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Yes! It definitely shouldn't be frozen still like it is now! ...At least, that's not how it was when I first got here? Ugh, I've done such a terrible job of taking care of it, it's so embarrassing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, everything's gonna be okay. So, we need to fix the big wheel up there, and to do that we need to find the missing parts."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Right... I do know where one of the parts is. It landed not too far away."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "But the rest all landed in different areas. I'm afraid you'll have to go and look for those..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Ahem! Now, as the caretaker and your mascot, I shall announce your respective adventure duties!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collei",
                    "T": "Umm... You can just be yourself if you want, no need to force the whole roleplaying thing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "...Oh, I see... Um, okay, so I was thinking that maybe Swordmaster Eula and Healer Collei could investigate the northern zone, if that's okay?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Fine by me. I was going to be looking for my cousin there anyway."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Collei",
                    "T": "I'll be your backup, Eula. I know you usually team up with Amber, so I'll try my best to fill her shoes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Eula",
                    "T": "Oh? Well this'll be fun. Let's see if a forest ranger can outperform an outrider."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Master Thief Kaeya and Mage Klee, if you could earmark some time in your busy schedules to search the west zone..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Earmark? What does that mean?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "It just means we mustn't forget to do it. Don't worry, we can handle that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "#Finally, we have our General, Miss Sangonomiya, and our Knight, {NICKNAME}. If there's no objections, please come with me to retrieve the first component."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Understood."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You have my sword!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Wow... Spoken like a true knight."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Hehe... Then for my part, my strategic mind is at your service."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Alright. Well, if anyone finds anything, come back here and we'll regroup."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Please take care while you're out on the road, and look after each other... especially our little mage here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "You got it! I'll take extra-special care of Kaeya."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "I'll be on my best behavior."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Okay, we'll leave it there for now. You two, please follow me."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
