    "4011312": {
        "Desc": "Talk to Idyia",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What is this thing, anyway? Some kind of gear?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And why's it so small? It doesn't look like it belongs in that huge wheel..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "It's hard to explain, but I assure you that it's definitely one of the components."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "So that leaves three more components missing..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Every journey begins with a first step. I think we're off to a good start, and things should keep going smoothly from here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Y—You really think so?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Of course, trust the General!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "I suppose you're right... she did manage to defeat class A at the Onmyou chamber, after all..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Um... You, uh, don't need to keep bringing that up!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "Anyway, thank you for all your help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "I'll take this and start trying to repair the Central Hub. You two may as well head back to town."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "*sigh* Why am I so clumsy? Once again, I was no help at all... The least I can do is try and handle the actual repairs."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "4011313": {
        "Desc": "Return to the Silver Bottle Courtyard",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Hmm..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "What's wrong, Kokomi?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I'm just a little confused... You mentioned that the Water Droplet showed you how to use the projector?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Can you tell me a little bit more about that? I'm so curious to know what happened."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, sure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Kokomi everything that happened earlier with Water Droplet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "I see..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, look! The wheel is spinning now."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aww, and now it's stopped again. Well, that didn't last long..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "It also wasn't spinning at the right speed. Before the incident, it spun much faster than that."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, so you saw it back when it was still working?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Yes. I arrived here a little earlier than the rest of you. But the incident took place not long after I entered."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Like Idyia said, it felt like the world was \"flipped upside down\"... I don't know how else to describe it... and I certainly don't want to experience it again."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "*sigh* It's no use... Seems it won't run until all the missing components are returned."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "For a moment there, when it started turning, I got excited... I thought that maybe the hub can work just fine without the other three..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Wishful thinking is only going to lead to disappointment, Idyia. Let's stick to the plan, we'll get there."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "#Hey, {M#Mr.}{F#Miss} Honorary Knight and Miss General are here! Oh, and our mascot!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "You beat us! I was sure we were gonna be the first ones back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Hey. How'd it go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Mission complete!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Where a knight's sword goes, victory soon follows!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "Haha. Impressive. I doubt you'd find many other knights of such caliber even among the Knights of Favonius."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "How about our Master Thief and Mage? Did you find anything?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "You bet! We made a huuuge discovery!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "The place we were trying to get to was blocked off. We couldn't see anything past it, and there was no way around."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "But then, just now, a huge canyon appeared outta nowhere... so we hurried back here!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "It appeared just now?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "#Come and see, {M#Mr.}{F#Miss} Honorary Knight! Let's go on a canyon adventure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "To the canyon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Idyia",
                    "T": "I'll sit this one out. I'm beat after trying to make those repairs... I need to take a break."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Miss General, you should come, too! You can hide behind me and give me smart advice while I protect you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Wonderful. It would be an honor to serve as adviser for our young mage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Hee-hee, let's go!!!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
