    "4011404": {
        "Desc": "Talk to everyone",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "The track is damaged up ahead. We need to make some repairs before we can go any further..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "Yep, looks like it's all reverted to a preprint state here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Sangonomiya Kokomi",
                    "T": "Do you know why that happened?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "Everything in this domain starts as a preprint and only takes shape after being illuminated by the Streaming Projector."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "But the Hydro Eidolon that forms the tracks here has been trapped in the print..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Kaeya",
                    "T": "So someone needs to go into the preprint and rescue the Hydro Eidolon. Right?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But the projector here's sealed off by a giant bubble."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "That's the Hydro Eidolon's way of protecting the device from damage... If the Streaming Projector broke, then we'd be seriously stuck."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aha! So for step one, we need Water Droplet to help!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hydro Eidolon",
                    "T": "Gurgle..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aww, it seems to really like that name!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Hydro Eidolon",
                    "T": "Gurgle!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "Um... Any volunteers for step two...?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Leave that to us. We know what to do!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
