    "4011414": {
        "Desc": "Return to the Torrential Twister's Cart Platform",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "Haddo and I have double-checked everything, it's all operating safely. You can go for a ride now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeroney",
                    "T": "Hold on a sec... Before we say goodbye, I have something I'd like to give you all."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeroney",
                    "T": "It's a rock climbing rope. We used it on our adventures to climb mountains and traverse many places."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh? But doesn't it mean a lot to you? Are you sure you want to give it to us?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeroney",
                    "T": "Yes, of course. Please take it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jeroney",
                    "T": "Thanks to Klee and everyone else's help, we realized that there is a special bond that keeps us together. Even though it's invisible, it's even more important than rope, and we can always hold on to it in tough situations."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Huh? I helped?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haddo",
                    "T": "Yes, Klee. You were a big help."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Even bigger than that huge thing in the middle of this place?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Ferdinand",
                    "T": "Yes, much bigger."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Wow, that's huge! I'm so happy!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haddo",
                    "T": "By the way, have you ever seen anything like the Choo-Choo Cart in the outside world?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Nope! Today was the first time I rode anything like it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haddo",
                    "T": "Is that so? *cough* I guess I'm not surprised. Seems you won't find a Streaming Projector anywhere else."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Haddo",
                    "T": "Be sure to come back and ride the Choo-Choo Carts again while you still have the chance."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Yep! I will!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
